oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Convention Corner '99 Denver, August 11-15
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Davis, Kelly
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Join us August 11-15 in Denver, Colorado for Convention '99 and the celebration of AFA's 25th Anniversary. This year promises to be the most exciting and fun convention yet! Don't miss this once a year opportunity to hear exceptional speakers in an array of fields such as bird breeding, nutrition, mutations, buying your first bird, and much more! Before the educational sessions begin, relax while AFA heads for the wild side - The Denver Zoo on Wednesday, August 11, 1999. The Zoo tour will offer a great BBQ lunch, behind the scenes tours, awesome animals and lots of fun. Be sure to attend.On Thursday, we will officially kick off Convention '99 with a ribbon cutting outside the exhibit hall. With over 55 exhibitors, you can shop until you drop!
